snippet.title: Disney Dreamlight Valley – April Update Sneak Peek
snippet.description:
Surprise! Just ahead of our Feb 16 update, we have a sneak peek at something a little further along the horizon...

Fresh from today's Nintendo Direct, get your first look at the beauty of the Lion King realm, coming in our April update! 🦁✨ Learn more here: https://disneydreamlightvalley.com/news/april-update-sneak-peek 

Play now!: http://www.disneydreamlightvalley.com/
